broadwick.data.readers

Class FullMovementsFileReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • broadwick.data.readers.DataFileReader
      • broadwick.data.readers.FullMovementsFileReader

  • public class FullMovementsFileReader
extends DataFileReader
    Reader for the files describing the full movements (i.e. those that specify both the departure location and the destination location of a movement)for the simulation. The movements are read and stored in internal databases for later use.
